item.description: Team Never Give up believe in our team approach to help others overcome various adversities. Our talents list of speakers have years of knowledge in mentoring people of all ages in their respective industries. Our mission statement: Purpose, Determination, Results is a trilogy that focuses on creating results by understands each individuals "Why" or Purpose and what we need to do in order to focus on their motivation or determination to meet their end goals.
